{{Quote|That cable? That's a vine?''"<br />"''It a ''kshyy'' vine is. Do not worry about its strength. It is strongerr than composite cable material, and cannot even by blasterrs be cut. Too, it is self-repairing.|[[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] and [[Ralrracheen]]|<ref name="Heir to the Empire">''[[Heir to the Empire]]''</ref>}}
'''''Kshyy'' vines''' were [[Plant/Legends|plants]] which grew on the [[Wroshyr tree/Legends|wroshyr trees]] of [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. The [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] hung sacrifices from one such vine to feed a [[Terentatek/Legends|terentatek]]. These vines were self-repairing vines, which could not be damaged even by blasters.

Liftcars on Kashyyyk were held in place and moved vertically by ''kshyy'' vines. Various fungi and parasites, if unchecked, could damage or break the vines, but the cars employed [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlifts]] as a backup.

